gapminder_1972<-gapminder %>%
  select(country, continent, year, lifeExp, pop, gdpPercap) %>%
  filter(year==1972)

1972 yl alt verileri ktalar/lkeler iin bar grafii

ggplot(gapminder_1972, aes(x=continent,fill=continent)) +
    geom_bar()

Her bir kta iin ort yaam srelerini hesaplayalm.

kta_yaam_sreleri<-gapminder %>%
  group_by(continent)%>%
  summarize(ort_yaam=mean(lifeExp))
              
kta_yaam_sreleri
## # A tibble: 5  2
##   continent ort_yaam

ktalarn ortalama yaam srelerini Bar grafikle gsterelim.

ggplot(kta_yaam_sreleri, aes(x=continent, y=ort_yaam)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity",fill="orange",color="yellow")

gdpPercap, country, year deikenlerinden oluan alt veri setini ekelim. Sadece lke==france olanlar filtreliyoruz.

gapminder_france<- gapminder %>%
  select(gdpPercap,year,country) %>%
  filter(country== 'France')

year=1972, gdpPercap deikeni iin histogram (olaslk younluk fonksiyonunun temsili gsterimi)

ggplot(gapminder_1972,aes(x=gdpPercap, fill=year))+
  geom_histogram()
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

deikenin younluk fonksiyonunu izdirelim

ggplot(gapminder_1972,aes(x=gdpPercap))+
  geom_density(color="blue")

1972 yl her bir kta iin ortalama yaam sresi karlatralm

ggplot(gapminder_1972,aes(x=continent, y=lifeExp, fill=continent))+
  geom_boxplot()

ggplot(gapminder_1972,aes(x=continent, y=lifeExp, colour=lifeExp, fill=continent))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_boxplot()

ktalarn yllara gre gdppercap deiimlerini karlatralm

gap_gdp<-gapminder %>%
         group_by(continent,year) %>%
         summarise(ortalama_gdp=mean(gdpPercap))
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'continent'. You can override using the
## `.groups` argument.
ggplot(gap_gdp,aes(x=year,y=ortalama_gdp,color=continent))+
  geom_line()

kta ve yllara gre ortalama yaam sresi karlatrma

gap_gdp<-gapminder %>%
         group_by(continent,year) %>%
         summarise(ortalama_mr=mean(lifeExp))
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'continent'. You can override using the
## `.groups` argument.
ggplot(gap_gdp,aes(x=year,y=ortalama_mr,color=continent))+
  geom_line()
